# alex-cv — core

Personal CV/portfolio: landing + three Rizzult case pages + 404.

**Routes (file-based):**

- `/` → `src/pages/index.vue`
- `/cases/rizzult-influencers`, `rizzult-talent-manager`, `rizzult-brands` → `src/pages/cases/{slug}.vue`
- 404 → `src/pages/[...path].vue`

**Commands:** `pnpm dev` | `pnpm build` | `pnpm preview` | `pnpm lint` | `pnpm format`

**Stack:** Vue 3 SFC, Vite 8, TypeScript, vue-router v5, Tailwind v4, pnpm.

**Entry:** `src/main.ts` → `./assets/main.css`, then mount `App.vue` with router. `@` → `src/`. DevTools via `vite-plugin-vue-devtools`.

See `CLAUDE.md` for full detail; architecture and conventions in sibling rules under `src/**`.
